sellerCard.description:
Hi, 
My name is Munawar and I am an experienced Developer that has worked in the technical field of Web Development. 

I have used many programming languages and worked on different Content Management Systems (CMS) like WordPress, Joomla, Shopify, and many more. 

In my years of experience, I have completed many successful projects in HTML, CSS, JS, bootstrap, PSD to HTML, PSD to Shopify, WordPress, Liquid, PHP, JSON, React, Node, Express, MongoDB, websites from scratch, and many more.

description.content:
Hi there! 

My name is MUNAWAR & I develop complete Shopify store, Shopify Website, Shopify Drop-shipping Store solutions that help my customers transform their dreams into reality.

Why Hire Me:

  • Shopify Drop-shipping Expert since 2013
  • 5+ years of experience in Shopify
  • 100% Free Support
  • 100% Client Satisfaction
  • 100% Professional Work
  • 100% On-time Delivery


IN THIS GIG I AM OFFERING THE FOLLOWING SERVICES :

  • THEME INSTALLATION.
  • THEME CUSTOMIZATION.
  • HEADER AND FOOTER SETUP.
  • ALL PAGES SETUP E.G. CONTACT US, ABOUT US, WISHLIST.
  • SETTING UP LOGIN OR SIGN UP.
  • ADDING SHIPPING OPTIONS.
  • DROP SHIPPING STORE.
  • PHYSICAL PRODUCTS OR DIGITAL PRODUCTS.
  • MAKING CATEGORIES OR COLLECTIONS.
  • ADDING PRODUCTS WITH DIFFERENT VARIANTS.
  • AND ALL SHOPIFY SERVICES.  


If you have any problem with Shopify or don't know about Shopify then don't worry I am here to consult you about everything in Shopify. You just need to contact me and I will be here for you.


THANKS!

REGARDS,

ABAIK_SOLUTIONS!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will You Fix Any Bug Issues ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can also fix any issue with your Shopify store.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you do my development in a test environment and then implement it to my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, Upon Request I will do the development First in the test environment.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you add customization settings in customize theme?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can add customization setting in customize option if that is not added by the theme developer. This will only added upon request and depends on the option it maybe extra charges.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is this final price or do you have any extra charges?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: It may have extra charges for some projects but not in all cases, special type of customization like complicated code editing, setting up extra options etc.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need from me?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I need the URL of your Shopify store and the login details.

questionsAndAnswers.question: In How many day will my website completed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I usually take 1 day to complete any project but if due to rush It can maximum take 3 days to 5 days.
